txt.en: You stow the rune-inscribed urns.\n\nOnce your exploration of Thuringwath is finished, you plan to deliver them to Mithrandir.
Rune-inscribed urns can be found at Aufaltor in Thuringwath.\n\nYou have discovered numerous urns bearing runic inscriptions in Aufaltor. You should collect a number of them for Mithrandir.
Rune-inscribed urns can be found at Aufaltor in Thuringwath.
You have collected many rune-inscribed urns at Aufaltor.
Within Aufaltor, many rune-inscribed urns of shadow rest among the Dead. Mithrandir may have an interest in them, for historical record.

Within Aufaltor, many rune-inscribed urns of shadow rest among the Dead. The urns are not of Gondorian-make, and though you can not read the runes, you shudder as your mind inevitably wanders to imagining whatever profane rituals the previous residents here may have carried out.\n\nThe vile inscriptions they bear may be of interest to Mithrandir.
